Loved his show and his specials, occasionally irritated by his take on a few things, yet glad he's brave enough to be honest about how he feels. His speech is, perfection, in an imperfect world. Gracious, yet cocky. Wise though irreverent. Both sacred and profane. There is something in everything, all is all! Thank you, Dave!
